          <article class="product-review" id="masa-pliabila-camping-profesionala-otel-si-lemn-impregnat-180x80-cm">
            <div class="product-review__header">
              <span class="section-tag">Premium</span>
              <h3>Masa Pliabila Camping Profesionala, Otel si Lemn Impregnat, 180x80 cm</h3>
              <div class="product-review__specs-grid">
